Package: scim-openvanilla
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends} libscim6 (>= 1.2.2)
Suggests: openvanilla-im-modules
Description: OpenVanilla loader for SCIM
 SCIM (Smart Common Input Method) is an input method platform on X11.  
 OpenVanilla (OV) is an input method (IM)/output filter (OF) framework 
 designed for better end-use text processing experiences.  It is divided
 into two major components: loader and modules.  This package is the loader
 that bridges OpenVanilla modules to the SCIM platform.
 .
 For development on OpenVanilla modules, please see the descrition of 
 package openvanilla-dev.
 .
 Homepage: http://openvanilla.org/


Package: openvanilla-dev
Architecture: all
Description: OpenVanilla framework(development files)
 OpenVanilla (OV) is an input method (IM)/output filter (OF) framework 
 designed for better end-use text processing experiences.  It is divided
 into two major components: loader and modules.  
 .
 This package is the framework for development on OpenVanilla modules.
 .
 For more information about OpenVanilla, please see http://openvanilla.org/.


Package: openvanilla-im-modules
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends} scim-openvanilla
Description: OpenVanilla input method modules
 OpenVanilla (OV) is an input method (IM)/output filter (OF) framework 
 designed for better end-use text processing experiences.  It is divided
 into two major components: loader and modules.  
 .
 This package contains the following input method modules:
   Array 30
   ChangJei
   Dayi3
   EHQ-Symbols
   Iroha
   Phoentic (Bopomofo)
   POJ-Holo
   Tibetan
 

